WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-IN

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Last year in June-July

00:00:08.677 --> 00:00:09.499
the right side front wheel

00:00:11.268 --> 00:00:12.326
it got damaged on impact

00:00:13.551 --> 00:00:15.000
and I had to give the car to service center

00:00:16.205 --> 00:00:17.498
and ofcourse claim insurance

00:00:18.639 --> 00:00:20.639
at that time my insurance provider was ICICI lombard

00:00:21.914 --> 00:00:23.129
and as you guys know watching my videos

00:00:24.014 --> 00:00:25.386
I did not have a very good experience with ICICI

00:00:27.550 --> 00:00:28.529
you guys can click on this link

00:00:30.001 --> 00:00:31.765
I have mentioned there in detail

00:00:32.835 --> 00:00:34.050
how you must avoid ICICI

00:00:36.573 --> 00:00:38.180
the folks in ICICI at that time

00:00:40.376 --> 00:00:41.591
reviewed the damage

00:00:42.440 --> 00:00:43.890
and one portion of the damage

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:46.090
they refused to approve the claim

00:00:48.208 --> 00:00:49.736
that claim was on the front bumper

00:00:50.446 --> 00:00:52.446
which got damaged and came out in the impact

00:00:54.708 --> 00:00:56.944
you guys can see how the damage looks at this point in time

00:00:58.193 --> 00:01:00.193
at that point last year the damage was not this bad

00:01:03.593 --> 00:01:05.907
ICICI is notorious in approving damage claims

00:01:07.169 --> 00:01:07.991
and since ICICI did not provide claim for this damage

00:01:08.832 --> 00:01:10.439
the service center folks somehow fixed the front bumper

00:01:13.286 --> 00:01:15.286
for the last few months I was facing issues with the bumper

00:01:15.787 --> 00:01:16.845
the bumper was coming out every time

00:01:17.901 --> 00:01:19.901
recently I completed this 3000 kms trip

00:01:21.844 --> 00:01:23.451
Hyderabad to Kolkata and back

00:01:24.735 --> 00:01:25.793
while coming back to Hyderabad

00:01:26.796 --> 00:01:28.482
there was a place where we were going through narrow lanes

00:01:29.433 --> 00:01:30.962
there was a ditch at the side of that road

00:01:33.491 --> 00:01:35.491
suddenly there was a person who came in the middle

00:01:36.622 --> 00:01:37.915
while trying to avoid hitting the person

00:01:39.551 --> 00:01:41.551
the front and rear left side tyres

00:01:43.116 --> 00:01:44.095
fell on that ditch

00:01:44.660 --> 00:01:45.160
and on impact

00:01:45.800 --> 00:01:46.622
the front bumper

00:01:47.645 --> 00:01:49.252
got more damaged as I showed you

00:01:50.179 --> 00:01:52.022
so I thought that this is the right time

00:01:54.305 --> 00:01:55.834
to claim insurance

00:01:56.876 --> 00:01:58.876
coz I have changed my insurance provider to Liberty

00:02:00.641 --> 00:02:02.091
I am making this video

00:02:02.588 --> 00:02:04.117
so that I can tell you guys

00:02:04.692 --> 00:02:06.378
the new insurance provider Liberty

00:02:08.282 --> 00:02:09.889
how is their overall claim process

00:02:11.738 --> 00:02:13.738
also how was my personal experience dealing with them

00:02:20.827 --> 00:02:23.612
I can find out did I do something right renewing with Liberty

00:02:25.863 --> 00:02:27.863
I have come today to the service center

00:02:29.284 --> 00:02:31.048
this time my point of contact here is Shiva

00:02:32.682 --> 00:02:34.682
he will help me with the insurance claim

00:02:36.542 --> 00:02:37.757
I have taken the inspection of the car

00:02:39.614 --> 00:02:41.614
we can claim insurance for the damage to the front bumper

00:02:44.324 --> 00:02:46.324
on my suggestion sir has taken Liberty insurance

00:02:47.789 --> 00:02:48.690
previously it was ICICI

00:02:49.927 --> 00:02:51.927
tell us, what is the claim process for Liberty?

00:02:52.974 --> 00:02:54.738
there is one claim form that needs to be filled

00:02:57.153 --> 00:02:58.333
and we have to give documents like insurance policy copy

00:02:58.333 --> 00:02:59.391
RCA, drivers license

00:03:01.153 --> 00:03:03.153
also owners PAN or Aadhar card copy

00:03:05.558 --> 00:03:07.558
it is a very easy process to complete the claim form

00:03:09.270 --> 00:03:11.270
we need to fill how, where, date, time of the accident details

00:03:11.843 --> 00:03:13.843
and once you sign, we will upload online for intimation

00:03:17.420 --> 00:03:19.420
mostly the work will be done within 1-2 days

00:03:21.177 --> 00:03:22.235
it will be approved fast

00:03:22.734 --> 00:03:23.635
this is a very simple process

00:03:24.474 --> 00:03:26.160
it won't be tedious like previous claims in ICICI?

00:03:26.888 --> 00:03:27.710
NO

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:30.901
this insurance is mostly there to help the customers

00:03:34.564 --> 00:03:36.093
So Shiva.. any other process pending now?

00:03:36.986 --> 00:03:38.044
No sir no other process pending

00:03:38.824 --> 00:03:39.803
the car is ready for delivery

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:43.049
there are no other formalities left all done

00:03:44.049 --> 00:03:45.421
ok, so if I complete the payment then I can take my car?

00:03:46.236 --> 00:03:46.822
yes its ready

00:03:47.430 --> 00:03:48.331
so this was a very easy claim process

00:03:50.276 --> 00:03:52.276
yes very simple process and the car got ready within 1-2 days

00:03:53.779 --> 00:03:54.994
thank you Shiva

00:03:54.994 --> 00:03:56.209
for suggesting this insurance company

00:03:56.589 --> 00:03:57.411
VISIT AGAIN SIR

00:03:58.561 --> 00:04:00.000
Sir this is a small complimentary gift for you

00:04:03.685 --> 00:04:05.685
I gave my car to the service center on Wednesday

00:04:07.098 --> 00:04:08.313
and today is Saturday

00:04:09.288 --> 00:04:10.581
so within a couple of days

00:04:11.610 --> 00:04:12.903
the repairing on the car was completed

00:04:13.797 --> 00:04:14.541
and it got delivered to me

00:04:15.633 --> 00:04:17.633
the overall experience with Liberty insurance

00:04:18.783 --> 00:04:20.155
that was sublime

00:04:21.683 --> 00:04:23.133
the experience with ICICI

00:04:23.875 --> 00:04:25.875
that I shared with you last year

00:04:26.885 --> 00:04:28.335
I never could imagine after that

00:04:30.532 --> 00:04:32.532
I can have a positive experience with a car insurance company

00:04:35.410 --> 00:04:37.410
I would highly recommend Liberty insurance

00:04:38.555 --> 00:04:40.555
and the PPS Renault service center at Madhapur

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:44.240
previously I have had good experiences with them

00:04:44.626 --> 00:04:46.076
and this time as well

00:04:47.043 --> 00:04:49.043
it was a complete and great experience

00:04:50.341 --> 00:04:51.870
there was nothing as such in the claim process this time

00:04:52.379 --> 00:04:53.908
I only filled up a form

00:04:55.586 --> 00:04:57.586
and provided the copy of my documents like RC, etc.

00:04:59.059 --> 00:05:00.666
then they just uploaded all the required information online

00:05:01.024 --> 00:05:03.024
in company portal and the survey was completed online as well

00:05:03.421 --> 00:05:04.949
and the approval was approved instantly the same day

00:05:07.181 --> 00:05:09.181
surveyor from insurance company comes and checks the car

00:05:09.538 --> 00:05:11.067
and all the related hassles

00:05:11.787 --> 00:05:12.881
no such thing was there this time around with Liberty

00:05:13.424 --> 00:05:15.424
it was a very smooth process and I'm very happy

00:05:17.140 --> 00:05:18.119
I also checked

00:05:18.477 --> 00:05:19.692
will the same process be valid

00:05:20.128 --> 00:05:21.264
only for such small claims

00:05:22.830 --> 00:05:24.123
or would it be the same process for bigger claims

00:05:24.549 --> 00:05:25.842
so Shiva told me

00:05:26.676 --> 00:05:28.676
probably if the claim is within 1 lakh

00:05:30.001 --> 00:05:32.001
it would be the same process of reviewing/approving online

